# Naming Conventions

## Workspace Names
- Lowercase, kebab-case: `backend`, `supply-chain`, `mobile-app`
- Letters, numbers, hyphens, underscores only (no spaces)
- Short and descriptive of the repo group's domain

## Task File Names
- With ticket: `[TICKET]-short-description.md` (e.g., `ABC-1234-fix-auth.md`)
- Without ticket: `short-description.md` (e.g., `fix-login-bug.md`)
- Lowercase, kebab-case, no spaces

## Documentation Names
- Descriptive of content: `database-guide.md`, `deployment-process.md`
- Lowercase, kebab-case

## Directory Structure
- `task-history/[workspace]/` for work logs
- `docs/[workspace]/` for reference guides
- `shared/` subdirectory for cross-workspace content
